sourcesContent: import React, { FunctionComponent, ReactElement } from 'react'; import { Box, Typography } from '@material-ui/core'; import '../styling/remixComponent.css'; type RemixComponentProps = { number: number, cover: string, title: string, artist: string } const RemixComponent: FunctionComponent = (props): ReactElement => { return( {props.number} {props.title} {props.artist} ) } export default RemixComponent;
